from re import sub
def clean(input_text):
    inputString = str(input_text).lower()
    WEB_URL_REGEX = r"""(?i)\b((?:https?:(?:/{1,3}|[a-z0-9%])|[a-z0-9.\-]+[.](?:com|net|org|edu|gov|mil|aero|asia|biz|cat|coop|info|int|jobs|mobi|museum|name|post|pro|tel|travel|xxx|ac|ad|ae|af|ag|ai|al|am|an|ao|aq|ar|as|at|au|aw|ax|az|ba|bb|bd|be|bf|bg|bh|bi|bj|bm|bn|bo|br|bs|bt|bv|bw|by|bz|ca|cc|cd|cf|cg|ch|ci|ck|cl|cm|cn|co|cr|cs|cu|cv|cx|cy|cz|dd|de|dj|dk|dm|do|dz|ec|ee|eg|eh|er|es|et|eu|fi|fj|fk|fm|fo|fr|ga|gb|gd|ge|gf|gg|gh|gi|gl|gm|gn|gp|gq|gr|gs|gt|gu|gw|gy|hk|hm|hn|hr|ht|hu|id|ie|il|im|in|io|iq|ir|is|it|je|jm|jo|jp|ke|kg|kh|ki|km|kn|kp|kr|kw|ky|kz|la|lb|lc|li|lk|lr|ls|lt|lu|lv|ly|ma|mc|md|me|mg|mh|mk|ml|mm|mn|mo|mp|mq|mr|ms|mt|mu|mv|mw|mx|my|mz|na|nc|ne|nf|ng|ni|nl|no|np|nr|nu|nz|om|pa|pe|pf|pg|ph|pk|pl|pm|pn|pr|ps|pt|pw|py|qa|re|ro|rs|ru|rw|sa|sb|sc|sd|se|sg|sh|si|sj|Ja|sk|sl|sm|sn|so|sr|ss|st|su|sv|sx|sy|sz|tc|td|tf|tg|th|tj|tk|tl|tm|tn|to|tp|tr|tt|tv|tw|tz|ua|ug|uk|us|uy|uz|va|vc|ve|vg|vi|vn|vu|wf|ws|ye|yt|yu|za|zm|zw)/)(?:[^\s()<>{}\[\]]+|\([^\s()]*?\([^\s()]+\)[^\s()]*?\)|\([^\s]+?\))+(?:\([^\s()]*?\([^\s()]+\)[^\s()]*?\)|\([^\s]+?\)|[^\s`!()\[\]{};:'".,<>?«»“”‘’])|(?:(?<!@)[a-z0-9]+(?:[.\-][a-z0-9]+)*[.](?:com|net|org|edu|gov|mil|aero|asia|biz|cat|coop|info|int|jobs|mobi|museum|name|post|pro|tel|travel|xxx|ac|ad|ae|af|ag|ai|al|am|an|ao|aq|ar|as|at|au|aw|ax|az|ba|bb|bd|be|bf|bg|bh|bi|bj|bm|bn|bo|br|bs|bt|bv|bw|by|bz|ca|cc|cd|cf|cg|ch|ci|ck|cl|cm|cn|co|cr|cs|cu|cv|cx|cy|cz|dd|de|dj|dk|dm|do|dz|ec|ee|eg|eh|er|es|et|eu|fi|fj|fk|fm|fo|fr|ga|gb|gd|ge|gf|gg|gh|gi|gl|gm|gn|gp|gq|gr|gs|gt|gu|gw|gy|hk|hm|hn|hr|ht|hu|id|ie|il|im|in|io|iq|ir|is|it|je|jm|jo|jp|ke|kg|kh|ki|km|kn|kp|kr|kw|ky|kz|la|lb|lc|li|lk|lr|ls|lt|lu|lv|ly|ma|mc|md|me|mg|mh|mk|ml|mm|mn|mo|mp|mq|mr|ms|mt|mu|mv|mw|mx|my|mz|na|nc|ne|nf|ng|ni|nl|no|np|nr|nu|nz|om|pa|pe|pf|pg|ph|pk|pl|pm|pn|pr|ps|pt|pw|py|qa|re|ro|rs|ru|rw|sa|sb|sc|sd|se|sg|sh|si|sj|Ja|sk|sl|sm|sn|so|sr|ss|st|su|sv|sx|sy|sz|tc|td|tf|tg|th|tj|tk|tl|tm|tn|to|tp|tr|tt|tv|tw|tz|ua|ug|uk|us|uy|uz|va|vc|ve|vg|vi|vn|vu|wf|ws|ye|yt|yu|za|zm|zw)\b/?(?!@)))"""
    inputString1 = sub(WEB_URL_REGEX, " _url_ ", inputString)  # removing url
    inputString2 = sub(r"(?:@[\w_]+)", " _mention_ ", inputString1)
    inputString3 = sub(r"(?:\#+[\w_]+[\w\'_\-]*[\w_]+)", " _hashtag_ ", inputString2)
    inputString4 = sub("\s+", " ", inputString3)
    inputString5 = sub(r"[^\s]+@([\w_-]+(?:(?:\.[\w_-]+)+))([\w.,@?^=%&:/~+#-]*[\w@?^=%&/~+#-])?", " _email_ ",
                       inputString4)  # replace email with _email_
    inputString6 = sub("\d+", " _number_ ", inputString5)  # remove numbers
    inputString7 = sub(r'(.)\1+', r'\1\1', inputString6)  # multiple occurrences of same word
    return inputString7.lower()

def get_word_freq(sent_li):
    word_freq_dict = dict()
    for i in sent_li:
        i = nltk.word_tokenize(i)
        for word in i:
            if word not in string.punctuation and word not in all_stops:
                if word in word_freq_dict:
                    word_freq_dict[word]+=1
                else:
                    word_freq_dict[word]=1
    return word_freq_dict

In [41]:
def get_model(input_shape, learning_rate):
        model = Sequential()
        model.add(Dense(2048,activation='relu',input_dim=input_shape))
        model.add(Dropout(rate=0.2))
        model.add(Dense(1024,activation='relu',input_dim=input_shape))
        model.add(Dropout(rate=0.2))
        model.add(Dense(512,activation='relu'))
        model.add(Dropout(rate=0.2))
        model.add(Dense(128,activation='relu'))
        model.add(Dropout(rate=0.2))
        model.add(Dense(1,activation='tanh'))
              
        adam_opt = optimizers.Adam(lr=learning_rate)
        model.compile(optimizer=adam_opt,loss='mean_absolute_error',metrics=['mean_absolute_error'])
        print('Model summary :', model.summary())
    
        return model
In [42]:
class Featuriser:
    def __init__(self,):
        self.__trained = False
        self.tfidf_vect = TfidfVectorizer(stop_words=nltk_words,)#ngram_range=(1, 3))
        
    def featuriser_train(self,data_li):
        if self.__trained == True:
            print('The model has already been trained, returning transformed features !!')
            feats = self.tfidf_vect.transform(data_li)#.toarray()
            return feats
        feats = self.tfidf_vect.fit_transform(data_li)#.toarray()
        print('Number of features are :',len(self.tfidf_vect.get_feature_names()))
        self.__trained = True
        return feats
